<h1>\{{eui-select}}</h1>

<div class="intro">
  A reimplementation of the standard browser select with added support for validation, error handling, and search.
</div>

<p>
  The select uses the poplist component to query the user's selection.
</p>
<p>
  The <em>poplist</em> makes use of list-view to hande large amounts of data without performance hickups. To make it easy to navigate for the user search support is provided. Simply start typing while the <em>poplist</em> is open to filter the options.
</p>

<div class="output">
  {{eui-select placeholder='Countries' labelPath='name' valuePath='code' optionsBinding='fullCountryList'}}
</div>

<p>
  The <em>poplist</em> prevents the page from scrolling while the cursor is over the poplist. Should the page scroll the poplist will be close automatically.
</p>


